		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			l The zoo is south of central Moonglow.
			l The zoo is south of the city.
			l If it wasn't for the zoo in southern Moonglow, the mages would have to trek into the wilds to look at these animals.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
