				l The Mages' Guilds are places those learned in the magic arts gather. If thou hast questions, any of the three are equally knowledgeable. At least two are within easy distance of a teleporter.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			l Moonglow's got lotsa Mages' Guilds. One's down south, one's out east and one's up north.
			l The three Mages' Guilds are all 'round the city's edge.
				l At least two Mages' Guilds are within easy distance of a teleporter.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
