ON=*teleporter*
	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			l Moonglow is a grand, vast city, and 'twould be problematic to walk from hither to yon all day. We've four teleporter locations, not counting the one in the center of the city.
			l Teleporters? Well, there's one near the Lycaeum, of course, one by the zoo, one near the eastern residence section, and one near the northern houses.
			l We've put a teleporter at each of the far flung edges of town: zoo and Lycaeum, and then the two residential areas.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 3
			l We got four teleporter locations, not countin' the one in the center of the city.
			l Teleporters? There's one near the Lycaeum, one by the zoo, one over near the eastern housing section, and one near the northern houses.
