	IF ( <COMPLEXITY.HIGH> || <COMPLEXITY.MEDIUM> )
		DORAND 3
			l Moonglow got its start, thou knowest, by studying the moons' manipulation of the ether. Our telescope furthers our education about the sky. If thou wishes to see it, head to the easternmost of the city.
			l Thou canst guess from our city's name that our scholars are intrigued by celestial objects. In the eastern part of the city, near the shore, we have the realms' largest eyeglass pointed at the sky.
			l There are certainly some schools of magic that ignore the heaven's influence, but in Moonglow it is studied intensely. Our telescope was custom made to scry for those things of most interest to mages.
		ENDDO
	ELSE
		DORAND 2
			l Our telescope is over in the east part of the city.
			l In the eastern part of the city, out near the shore, we got a telescope.
		ENDDO
	ENDIF
